title: Call Me Coach
description: Katie and the Union discuss what animals/dinosaurs would be best at playing volleyball. “Football” is “back” (21:17). Simone Biles continues to be awesome (25:53). Jeopardy has a new host (33:15). Don’t spook the horses (42:08). Put some respect on Jason Garrett’s (nick)name (52:28). What do you eat when you’re sad (1:05:27)? What’s the perfect level of famousness (1:13:04)? What mascot would you like to go camping with (1:20:23)? Finally, what music do you listen to after a long day (1:26:42)?
